            , 20 ditto, of St. Ann's, '' Westminster, spinster, are very desirous to enter '' into the holy state of matrimony, without publication '' of banns, they solemnly declare there '' is no lawful cause to the contrary, &amp;c.</p>
               <p>'' I do hereby consent the said marriage may '' be solemnized in St. John Baptist's chappel, '' in the Savoy.</p>
